- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the semantics and termination of logic programs with function symbols.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also a likely category as the paper discusses the evaluation of logic programs.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as logic programming is often used in AI applications.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper proposes new criteria for checking termination of logic programs.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the analysis of program structure and safety criteria.
